<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1272' id='t-1272'>Picture this:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='2649' id='t-2649'>It's Monday morning,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='3742' id='t-3742'>you're at the office,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='4861' id='t-4861'>you're settling in for the day at work,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='6615' id='t-6615'>and this guy that you sort of 
recognize from down the hall,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='9437' id='t-9437'>walks right into your cubicle</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='11273' id='t-11273'>and he steals your chair.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='12675' id='t-12675'>Doesn't say a word —</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='13917' id='t-13917'>just rolls away with it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='15305' id='t-15305'>Doesn't give you any information
