<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='58816' id='t-58816'>you go back to your desk,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='60499' id='t-60499'>and you stand at your 
desk and you say,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='62008' id='t-62008'>&quot;Boy, I wish I had those two hours back,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='64671' id='t-64671'>like I wish I had my chair back.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='66674' id='t-66674'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:19
