<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='68180' id='t-68180'>Every day, we allow our coworkers,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='70751' id='t-70751'>who are otherwise very, 
very nice people,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='72965' id='t-72965'>to steal from us.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='74632' id='t-74632'>And I'm talking about something far 
more valuable than office furniture.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='78710' id='t-78710'>I'm talking about time. Your time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='81739' id='t-81739'>In fact, I believe that</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='84392' id='t-84392'>we are in the middle
