<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='86877' id='t-86877'>of a terrible new illness
known as MAS:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='91917' id='t-91917'>Mindless Accept Syndrome.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='94190' id='t-94190'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='96084' id='t-96084'>The primary symptom of 
