</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:01
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='110936' id='t-110936'>Meetings are important, right?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='113323' id='t-113323'>And collaboration is key to 
the success of any enterprise.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='116269' id='t-116269'>And a well-run meeting can yield 
really positive, actionable results.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='119662' id='t-119662'>But between globalization</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='121420' id='t-121420'>and pervasive information technology,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='123735' id='t-123735'>the way that we work</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='125406' id='t-125406'>has really changed dramatically 
