<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='170688' id='t-170688'>And everybody leaves very angry.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='173114' id='t-173114'>It's kind of funny.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='174903' id='t-174903'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='176486' id='t-176486'>Let's take a quick look.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='178638' id='t-178638'>(Video) Our goal today is to come to an 
